{"tid":1375398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【721】港鐵公開閉路電視截圖還原18分鐘襲擊經過","createTime":"2019-07-28T05:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T05:14:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f87b1989a5cfd0db0b2788e60fd6cb3fa3f3bc","tid":1375398,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"西鐵元朗站於7月21日出現大批白衣人士襲擊事件，港鐵在事件中被批評妄顧市民安全，沒有職員協助，亦沒有即時將列車駛離月台。港鐵昨晚（27日）發放當晚的閉路電視截圖，重整事發經過，指出當晚10時57分，有乘客阻礙車門關閉，職員到月台協助；10時59分，車務控制中心安排「清客」，直至11時06分開始出現打鬥事件。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵車務總監劉天成昨晚（27日）向員工發出5頁信，並附上5張閉路電視截圖及時序解釋當晚情況。<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2412699/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2412699%2F&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpx5CyLKXDv55u35dva0wydI%3D&h=bcff8ba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2412699/</a>"},{"pid":"ec31b5675d26a8492d49836e995e2f5304cc1ec2","tid":1375398,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:03:45.000Z","msg":"10時55分<br />\n<br />\n往屯門方向列車抵達元朗站，列車如常上落客，月台未有襲擊事件發生。車長完成月台職務後準備開車，但發現有乘客阻礙車門，導致車門未能關上。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGbVaaT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGbVaaT.jpg&h=8c63e4a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ed1e8e4cfd22a3e0d14cd8453ebc17a674c1319","tid":1375398,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"10時57分<br />\n<br />\n有乘客不斷進出車廂，繼續阻礙車門。車務控制中心安排車站職員前往月台協助，嘗試將車門關上，但未能成功。<br />\n<br />\n10時59分<br />\n<br />\n車門仍未能成功關上，車務控制中心按相關程序授權列車車長，根據車務安排「清客」，再安排另一列車接載月台上的乘客，當時車長作出有關廣播 。而月台仍未見有襲擊事件發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WZ25xpk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWZ25xpk.jpg&h=1d3e7143&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfdb11777d2b51e98eedfffeb091fb960101167b","tid":1375398,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:04:50.000Z","msg":"11時06分<br />\n有大批人士從大堂湧上月台，然後走入車廂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnrBD4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnrBD4x.jpg&h=a30ee179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n11時07分<br />\n車長收到乘客報告指月台發生打鬥，車長即時通知車務控制中心，並留意到有人繼續阻礙車門，無法即時將列車駛離車站。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8RAZBRe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8RAZBRe.jpg&h=cbd002ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aea97e3e3cae4925021acf01b0f93f4e57bf9f44","tid":1375398,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:05:45.000Z","msg":"11時13分<br />\n經過多次嘗試後，車門成功關上，之後列車駛離月台。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6PaiSpH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6PaiSpH.jpg&h=cfb623b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">從閉路電視時序中可見，白衣人進入車廂襲擊歷時約7分鐘</span>。面對連日來的批評，劉天成強調當晚港鐵職員在危急情況下，已經克盡己任，保障乘客安全。<br />\n<br />\n我認為當晚大家已經盡了最大努力，展現了各崗位的專業，盡力化解危機。<br />\n<br />\n他又澄清，沒有任何涉事職員因此受到處分或受傷，而當晚值班的女車長，港鐵已安排專人慰問及給予特別有薪假期讓她休息；並呼籲外界不要對港鐵員工作出滋擾行為，包括洩露個人及其家人資料。"},{"pid":"87214c63c2bad808d258dc52eaec643100ae2563","tid":1375398,"uid":35746,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:06:25.000Z","msg":"最大問題係上邊一早打緊呢<br />\n<br />\n死都唔認低估左件事"},{"pid":"fcb4615498e87a7a4b257aadd7e5f2025cce8588","tid":1375398,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3f86c84846fb009bd1351408e7392faf2d038a","tid":1375398,"uid":171874,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">公開埋車站大堂 其他角度cctv先啦<br />\n<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n不分化<br />\n不割蓆<br />\n不譴責<br />\n對準政權<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"ea6acdb2b1d4e69ec5ccf1bcdedce08e720bf6d1","tid":1375398,"uid":48521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:11:05.000Z","msg":"大堂呢"},{"pid":"94aa793bb26042385f8a135d1fe50bebcaf7c4b0","tid":1375398,"uid":282490,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:12:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">成個星期鳩縮。但車長一話要罷工, 就急急腳整D所謂證據黎cool down?</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拿！都話罷工有用架啦</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"bb864eb8000d450ec49924540f69df585b9b5926","tid":1375398,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1751228c53c2b1f0845a51c40442d9a1375400","tid":1375398,"uid":43678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T05:14:48.000Z","msg":"11:05前已經打到上月台<br />\n<br />\n11:03車長已經廣播部車暫停行駛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}